                     <interp inst="t18580510-557-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Steal<lb></lb>ing 1 watch, value 14<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the property of <persName id="t18580510-name-381" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18580510-name-381" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
